            <text>
                <body>
                    <div type="edition">
                        <div type="textpart">
                            <ab>I fratelli <persName key="#Other_clerics"><name ref="Contulinus"
                                >Gontulino</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_clerics">chierico</rs> e <persName><name ref="Ildebrandus"
                                >Ildebrando</name></persName> del <persName>fu <name ref="Gherardus"
                                >Gherardo</name></persName> e la madre <persName><name ref="Pluma"
                                >Piuma</name></persName>, vedova del suddetto Gherardo e figlia del
                            <persName>fu <name ref="Ursus">Orso</name></persName>, con il consenso
                        dei figli e mundualdi Gontulino chierico, Ildebrando e <persName><name
                                ref="Rainerius">Ranieri</name></persName>, vendono a <persName><name
                                ref="Benbonus">Bembone</name></persName> del <persName>fu <name
                                ref="Benbonus">Bembone</name></persName>, tres portionis di un
                        appezzamento di terra, quod est orto, posta foras <rs key="#Cities"
                            >civitatis</rs> ista <placeName ref="#places/4" key="#Cities"
                            >Lucense</placeName> ubi dicitur <placeName ref="#places/4">a
                            Pulia</placeName>, <rs key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions"
                            >confinante</rs> uno capo cum uno lato in via plubica, alio capo con
                        terra del <rs key="#Priests">prete</rs>
                        <persName key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions #Priests"><name ref="Morus"
                                >Moro</name></persName>, alio lato con terra del suddetto prete Moro
                        e con terra di <persName key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions"><name
                                ref="Wido">Guido</name></persName> figlio di <persName key="#Monks"
                                ><name ref="Raginmundus">Raimondo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Monks">monaco</rs>, per una misura complessiva di 9 staia et
                        etriam portionem de scalas una con tutte le sue dipendenze, ricevendo <rs
                            key="#Meritum/launechild #Jewels">merito annulo uno de auro</rs> pro 110
                        soldi. Chiedono al <rs key="#Writer #Other_palatine_officer #Notary">notaio
                            del sacro palazzo</rs>
                        <persName key="#Writer #Other_palatine_officer #Notary"><name ref="Paulus"
                                >Paolo</name></persName> la stesura della cartula. Actum Luca. <rs
                            key="#Witness">Testimoni</rs> sottoscrittori: <persName key="#Witness"
                                ><name ref="Garofalus">Garofalo</name></persName> del <persName>fu
                                <name ref="Villanus">Villano</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Hubertus">Uberto</name></persName> del
                            <persName>fu <name ref="Bonitius">Bonaccio</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Anselmus">Anselmo</name></persName> del
                            <persName>fu <name ref="Andreas">Andrea</name></persName>. <rs
                            key="#Copyist">Copiatore</rs>: <persName key="#Copyist #Notary"><name
                                ref="Hugo">Ugo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius dom. reg</rs>. <rs key="#Witness">Testimoni</rs>
                        sottoscrittori: <persName key="#Witness #Other_palatine_officer #Notary"
                                ><name ref="Bonifacius">Bonifacio</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_palatine_officer #Notary">notarius sacri palatii</rs>,
                            <persName key="#Witness #Notary"><name ref="Ildebrandus"
                                >Ildebrando</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius dom. reg.</rs></ab>
                        </div>
